node.text: We've accepted the #ALLINCHALLENGE and we’re throwing a bbq and giving back to a charity of your choice with YOU! Go to the link in our bio and let’s all make a positive impact during this very difficult time. We challenge @daviddobrik @lewiscapaldi and @lewishamilton to go ALL IN. Donations will benefit @nokidhungry, @mealsonwheelsamerica and #americasfoodfund which benefits @feedingamerica and @wckitchen ❤️

node.text: I’m consistently in awe of you guys. You always show up for us no matter what. Thank you so much to everyone who had a hand in this tour. Best fans in the world. #HappinessBeginsTour
